OL,3,CBlind woman left fearing for her life
OL,4,Cas rubbish blocks pavements
OL,6,FOngoing bin strikes have turned
OL,7,FBirmingham's pavements into an
OL,8,F"assault course" - as ITV News
OL,9,FCentral's Laurence Griffin reports.
OL,11,FPiles of uncollected rubbish have
OL,12,Fblocked pavements in Birmingham,
OL,13,Fcreating a hazard for people with
OL,14,Fsight loss or a disability.
OL,16,FIt comes after an indefinite bin
OL,17,Fstrike by Unite the Union members over
OL,18,Fpay and working roles entered its
OL,19,Fthird week.
