OL,3,CBlind woman left fearing for her life
OL,4,Cas rubbish blocks pavements
OL,6,FPerm Bhachu, who is blind and uses a
OL,7,Flong cane to walk, told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral rubbish blocking her way has
OL,9,Fforced her to walk in the road,
OL,10,Fleaving her fearing for her life.
OL,12,FShe said: "It's like an assault
OL,13,Fcourse. You can do it if you're fully
OL,14,Fsighted, but if you've got very
OL,15,Flimited vision or have other mobility
OL,16,Fissues it's very difficult and
OL,17,Fdangerous.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
