OL,3,CBlind woman left fearing for her life
OL,4,Cas rubbish blocks pavements
OL,6,F"There are times where I'm trying to
OL,7,Fwalk, I've been wobbly on my feet, and
OL,8,Fto be totally honest, I've thought: 'I
OL,9,Fcan't do this' and I've turned back
OL,10,Fand I've gone home.
OL,12,F"I feel socially isolated, my
OL,13,Fanxieties are through the roof.
OL,15,F"When you hear vehicles coming past so
OL,16,Fclose when you're in the road, you
OL,17,Fthink: 'is this me now, is it my
OL,18,Ftime?'"
