OL,4,Cas rubbish blocks pavements
OL,6,FAdvice on Birmingham City Council's
OL,7,Fwebsite suggests residents leave their
OL,8,Fbins out to be collected until they
OL,9,Fare eventually taken, as it tries to
OL,10,Ftake them as soon as it can.
OL,12,FThe result is pavements lined with
OL,13,Fbins waiting to be collected, creating
OL,14,Fa stench and an annoyance for all
OL,15,Fresidents, but a potentially dangerous
OL,16,Fset of obstacles for people with sight
OL,17,Floss or other mobility issues.
