OL,4,Cas rubbish blocks pavements
OL,6,FCllr Majid Mahmood, Cabinet member for
OL,7,Fthe environment at Birmingham City
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "We have street
OL,9,Fcleaning crews that are monitoring all
OL,10,Fthe hotspots.
OL,12,F"We're making sure the footpaths are
OL,13,Fclear for vulnerable people,
OL,14,Fespecially those who are visually
OL,15,Fimpaired, wheelchair users, children
OL,16,Fand elderly people."
