OL,4,Cas rubbish blocks pavements
OL,6,FCate Burke, CEO of sight loss charity
OL,7,FFocus Birmingham, said: "Having a
OL,8,Fdisability is hard enough already,
OL,9,Ftheir lives are stressful enough as it
OL,10,Fis.
OL,12,F"People we support have complex needs
OL,13,Fincluding sight loss, hearing loss,
OL,14,Faccessibility needs - the bin strikes
OL,15,Fare impacting on everyone."
OL,17,FThe indefinite strike by Unite the
OL,18,FUnion has continuing, after crunch
OL,19,Ftalks with the council ended with
OL,20,Fworkers being threatened with
OL,21,Fcompulsory redundancy.
