OL,3,CBlind woman left fearing for her life
OL,4,Cas rubbish blocks pavements
OL,6,FUnite the Union said: "The disruption
OL,7,Fto Birmingham's refuse service is
OL,8,Fentirely the fault of a heartless
OL,9,Fcouncil which has slashed pay without
OL,10,Fa thought to the effect it is having
OL,11,Fon workers and their families.
OL,13,F"The council could end this dispute
OL,14,Ftomorrow by agreeing to a decent rate
OL,15,Fof pay.
OL,17,F"Instead, it is trying to force
OL,18,Fdedicated workers onto levels barely
OL,19,Fabove the minimum wage while
OL,20,Fundertaking a difficult and highly
OL,21,Fdemanding job in all weathers."
